WEBVTT

00:21.184 --> 00:22.464
笙ｪThat day笙ｪ

00:22.880 --> 00:24.448
笙ｪNothing stays together forever笙ｪ

00:24.448 --> 00:25.792
笙ｪI've quit romance笙ｪ

00:26.218 --> 00:27.920
笙ｪWho hasn't failed again笙ｪ

00:27.920 --> 00:31.424
笙ｪCrying in death笙ｪ

00:31.424 --> 00:34.016
笙ｪAnd in life笙ｪ

00:34.432 --> 00:36.370
笙ｪEven now笙ｪ

00:36.672 --> 00:38.656
笙ｪWe keep learning笙ｪ

00:38.656 --> 00:39.680
笙ｪIt's no surprise笙ｪ

00:39.744 --> 00:42.144
笙ｪBeing happy is so hard笙ｪ

00:42.144 --> 00:43.968
笙ｪWeirdly, I became a role model笙ｪ

00:44.736 --> 00:46.688
笙ｪOn the day we met again, we said hi笙ｪ

00:46.688 --> 00:52.896
笙ｪIt was a reminder,
a test, and a complaint笙ｪ

00:52.896 --> 00:56.003
笙ｪWho can do anything without regret笙ｪ

00:56.003 --> 00:59.424
笙ｪI am all right笙ｪ

01:00.480 --> 01:05.074
笙ｪMay you live in peace笙ｪ

01:05.074 --> 01:07.456
笙ｪLet the world roar笙ｪ

01:07.456 --> 01:09.732
笙ｪSounds like a carnival笙ｪ

01:09.732 --> 01:14.453
笙ｪBeing alive is never dull笙ｪ

01:14.453 --> 01:18.830
笙ｪHow wonderful to be free笙ｪ

01:18.830 --> 01:23.485
笙ｪI became even better without you笙ｪ

01:23.485 --> 01:25.824
笙ｪNothing can be perfect笙ｪ

01:25.824 --> 01:28.224
笙ｪWe bless each other in pain笙ｪ

01:28.224 --> 01:34.234
笙ｪWe nod and smile笙ｪ

01:35.328 --> 01:36.288
笙ｪMay we both be well笙ｪ

01:36.288 --> 01:41.024
= Love's Ambition=

01:41.232 --> 01:43.792
=Episode 7=

02:06.077 --> 02:06.916
Yu Yiming?

02:08.917 --> 02:09.936
I'll try the eyeshadow.

02:12.836 --> 02:13.357
Gone?

02:15.237 --> 02:15.876
I'm right here.

02:16.716 --> 02:17.396
What do you want?

02:18.116 --> 02:19.237
I'll try the eyeshadow.

02:20.757 --> 02:21.237
Go ahead.

02:25.156 --> 02:26.757
This color looks nice.

02:27.156 --> 02:28.556
Could you get me a lipstick?

02:28.676 --> 02:29.357
Another color.

02:29.716 --> 02:30.917
I used No.103 yesterday.

02:30.996 --> 02:31.957
Get me No.105 today.

02:40.517 --> 02:41.116
It looks good.

02:41.237 --> 02:41.996
I'm leaving. Bye.

02:42.556 --> 02:43.996
Wait. It does look good.

02:44.436 --> 02:45.957
Why don't you buy one of the things

02:45.996 --> 02:46.957
you just tried?

02:47.197 --> 02:49.197
Why? I use the testers every time.

02:50.156 --> 02:51.357
It's been a week, Miss.

02:51.477 --> 02:53.797
Whether it's windy or pouring rain,

02:53.957 --> 02:55.556
you'd show up at 5 PM sharp

02:55.596 --> 02:56.957
to freeload makeup.

02:57.077 --> 02:58.396
People might think you're here

02:58.436 --> 02:59.357
clocking in for work.

02:59.957 --> 03:00.676
An eyebrow pencil

03:00.676 --> 03:02.077
only costs six yuan,

03:02.077 --> 03:03.276
and you won't even buy one?

03:03.600 --> 03:04.077
Wait.

03:04.396 --> 03:06.037
What do you mean "freeload makeup"?

03:06.396 --> 03:07.317
I need to try them on

03:07.317 --> 03:08.477
before knowing what to buy.

03:08.876 --> 03:09.436
Besides,

03:09.637 --> 03:11.276
you don't limit the makeup trials.

03:12.770 --> 03:14.064
(Trials up to 6 times a week.)

03:16.197 --> 03:17.757
I never saw this before.

03:18.357 --> 03:20.116
This rule was made specifically for you.

03:21.197 --> 03:21.917
I just won't buy.

03:22.156 --> 03:22.876
So what?

03:23.876 --> 03:24.596
Save it.

03:24.676 --> 03:26.116
This is consumer fraud!

03:26.637 --> 03:27.676
I'll report you!

03:28.156 --> 03:29.436
Focus on your job. Bye.

03:47.197 --> 03:47.757
Mom.

03:48.676 --> 03:49.757
I transferred the money.

03:49.797 --> 03:50.517
Did you see it?

03:52.596 --> 03:54.517
Don't be frugal with it,

03:55.317 --> 03:57.197
calculating every egg for breakfast.

03:57.237 --> 03:58.317
It's not expensive!

03:58.957 --> 04:00.996
I know you work hard for the money.

04:01.477 --> 04:02.716
Being alone in Jingzhou,

04:03.116 --> 04:05.077
your health matters most.

04:06.957 --> 04:08.676
I told you I can earn enough.

04:09.116 --> 04:10.836
You don't know how much I make daily.

04:11.037 --> 04:11.797
I have everything.

04:11.876 --> 04:12.757
Okay, okay, okay.

04:13.037 --> 04:14.436
I know you're capable.

04:15.276 --> 04:17.437
But take care of yourself.

04:31.317 --> 04:32.396
Wh-What are those?

04:34.557 --> 04:35.997
These are all the testers you tried.

04:38.077 --> 04:39.836
I brought you some new ones.

04:39.877 --> 04:41.877
Do your makeup at home from now on.

04:41.916 --> 04:42.957
Don't come to the counter.

04:47.437 --> 04:49.036
If you keep pestering me there,

04:49.077 --> 04:50.356
I'll only be serving you.

04:50.396 --> 04:51.276
How will I make money?

05:07.637 --> 05:08.557
It's almost expired.

05:16.677 --> 05:17.796
The warehouse is so hot.

05:18.836 --> 05:20.957
Qiao Lin, we're short-staffed now.

05:21.117 --> 05:22.036
Can you do dispatch?

05:22.236 --> 05:22.796
I can.

05:23.997 --> 05:24.432
These.

05:25.077 --> 05:25.584
Great.

05:25.836 --> 05:27.077
Let me help you.

05:27.156 --> 05:27.757
Thank you.

05:29.877 --> 05:30.596
Wait. Wait.

05:30.677 --> 05:31.197
Phone call.

05:31.408 --> 05:31.957
Okay.

05:32.276 --> 05:32.916
I can do it.

05:34.156 --> 05:35.036
- Wait for me.
- Okay.

05:36.396 --> 05:36.916
Mr. Zhang.

05:38.877 --> 05:39.637
An HQ meeting?

05:40.476 --> 05:41.437
Got it. Be right there.

05:45.677 --> 05:46.197
What's wrong?

05:47.476 --> 05:48.396
Sorry. It's nothing.

05:48.476 --> 05:48.916
I'm okay.

05:49.557 --> 05:50.396
I told you to wait.

05:50.437 --> 05:51.356
Be careful, will you?

05:51.437 --> 05:51.997
Sorry.

05:51.997 --> 05:52.396
My bad.

05:58.077 --> 05:59.437
Go to the hospital now.

06:00.276 --> 06:01.557
Just go. Leave it to me.

06:02.557 --> 06:03.437
Sorry, sir.

06:04.476 --> 06:05.757
Th-Then I'll go first.

06:05.916 --> 06:06.796
- Just go.
- I'm so sorry.

06:09.437 --> 06:11.036
Works a little and demands payment.

06:18.236 --> 06:19.236
I got it scheduled.

06:19.757 --> 06:21.236
A top specialist appointment.

06:21.716 --> 06:22.476
Your turn soon.

06:22.992 --> 06:23.952
(No. 37 Qiao Lin)

06:24.757 --> 06:25.716
Thanks, Guan.

06:26.197 --> 06:26.677
Sure thing.

06:28.356 --> 06:29.197
I'm okay. I'm okay.

06:29.356 --> 06:30.077
We live together.

06:30.317 --> 06:31.356
We help each other out.

06:31.957 --> 06:33.836
If you ever need any help,

06:33.877 --> 06:35.036
you must tell me.

06:38.437 --> 06:39.317
Alright, I'm leaving.

06:39.356 --> 06:39.957
Back to stream.

06:39.997 --> 06:40.916
Leaving so soon?

06:41.677 --> 06:42.276
I need money

06:42.437 --> 06:43.757
to buy you bone broth.

06:44.877 --> 06:45.437
Love you!

06:45.637 --> 06:46.077
Going now.

06:46.197 --> 06:46.637
Good luck.

06:46.757 --> 06:47.197
Bye.

06:48.836 --> 06:49.317
Wait here.

06:50.356 --> 06:52.637
Now calling No. 37, Qiao Lin

06:52.836 --> 06:54.077
to Examination Room 4.

06:54.716 --> 06:55.156
Hold her.

06:56.517 --> 06:57.836
God, will it hurt?

06:58.877 --> 06:59.356
It's okay.

06:59.596 --> 07:00.396
Relax your muscles.

07:01.317 --> 07:02.637
You'll feel it, but hold on.

07:08.796 --> 07:09.156
Well?

07:11.596 --> 07:12.156
That's it?

07:14.077 --> 07:14.637
Check it out.

07:15.197 --> 07:16.716
It seems... better now.

07:17.117 --> 07:17.757
Help her up.

07:18.557 --> 07:19.197
Move it around.

07:19.356 --> 07:19.957
Don't force it.

07:20.677 --> 07:21.637
Okay, thank you.

07:24.356 --> 07:24.957
I feel better.

07:25.836 --> 07:26.916
I've realigned it.

07:27.476 --> 07:29.117
No heavy lifting for three months,

07:30.236 --> 07:31.077
and don't overuse it.

07:32.276 --> 07:34.036
Otherwise, you might re-dislocate.

07:34.957 --> 07:36.117
So... it heals this fast?

07:36.156 --> 07:37.197
Will it hurt again?

07:37.716 --> 07:39.036
If it hurts again later,

07:39.117 --> 07:40.317
I'll come straight to you.

07:40.557 --> 07:42.317
I won't pay the registration fee.

07:45.396 --> 07:46.557
You really haven't changed.

07:50.197 --> 07:50.757
Qiao Lin.

07:56.557 --> 07:57.356
Yu Yiming?

07:57.546 --> 08:00.176
(Yu Yiming)

08:00.176 --> 08:02.000
(City ranking: No. 1)

08:02.957 --> 08:05.557
Feels like we're growing apart.

08:06.276 --> 08:07.197
Don't be sad.

08:07.236 --> 08:08.236
We're all repeating.

08:08.276 --> 08:09.156
We can hang out.

08:09.997 --> 08:10.317
Exactly.

08:10.437 --> 08:11.476
Think about it again.

08:11.517 --> 08:12.517
Feel any better?

08:15.036 --> 08:16.596
I actually feel worse.

08:16.916 --> 08:18.557
I'll give you drugs for the pain.

08:19.396 --> 08:20.796
You might not feel anything now,

08:21.117 --> 08:22.557
but in 2-3 hours,

08:22.796 --> 08:23.476
it might hurt.

08:24.156 --> 08:25.396
Take meds if it's mild.

08:25.877 --> 08:27.517
If severe, come for an X-ray

08:27.836 --> 08:29.276
to check for soft tissue effusion.

08:29.557 --> 08:29.997
Okay.

08:30.637 --> 08:31.356
Thank you.

08:34.397 --> 08:35.157
Been here long?

08:35.917 --> 08:38.636
I arrived about two months ago.

08:39.077 --> 08:39.476
You live?

08:39.917 --> 08:42.636
I share an apartment with two friends.

08:43.157 --> 08:43.557
Girls.

08:45.557 --> 08:46.516
It's set back now.

08:46.917 --> 08:47.917
But if any issues arise,

08:48.077 --> 08:49.157
come see me immediately.

08:50.116 --> 08:50.917
No registration fee.

08:53.476 --> 08:54.836
Daily life will be inconvenient.

08:55.636 --> 08:56.756
Contact your parents?

08:57.356 --> 08:58.596
They're back in our hometown.

08:59.557 --> 09:00.236
Qiao Yan?

09:04.157 --> 09:04.677
Qiao Yan.

09:05.876 --> 09:06.797
My letter.

09:07.397 --> 09:08.116
Did you read it?

09:10.037 --> 09:10.756
Take it back.

09:12.957 --> 09:13.476
Yu Yiming.

09:13.876 --> 09:15.317
I came today to tell you

09:16.957 --> 09:17.957
I don't want to date.

09:18.397 --> 09:20.236
I just want to focus on studying.

09:20.557 --> 09:21.957
Other things aren't in my plans.

09:22.236 --> 09:23.397
I won't disturb your studies.

09:24.317 --> 09:25.756
I just wanted to say I like you.

09:25.797 --> 09:26.636
I don't like you.

09:41.077 --> 09:42.516
She goes by Xu Yan now.

09:43.437 --> 09:44.277
Ever been in touch?

09:44.957 --> 09:45.677
Have you?

09:47.797 --> 09:48.596
No.

09:49.557 --> 09:51.116
She came here for college, right?

09:51.636 --> 09:52.077
Yes.

09:52.876 --> 09:54.557
But she's too busy with work now.

09:54.836 --> 09:55.756
My injury is fine.

09:55.756 --> 09:56.437
I'm alright.

09:56.756 --> 09:58.037
Bone injuries are serious.

09:58.317 --> 09:59.636
Trust your doctor's advice.

10:00.037 --> 10:01.116
If it's awkward for you,

10:01.836 --> 10:02.636
give me her number.

10:02.756 --> 10:03.356
I'll call her.

10:03.596 --> 10:04.636
No, that's unnecessary.

10:14.512 --> 10:16.944
(Jingzhou Yuekang Hospital)

10:18.876 --> 10:20.596
I don't think she'll come.

10:20.636 --> 10:21.756
Her work keeps her occupied.

10:22.476 --> 10:24.197
You don't need to stay with me.

10:24.236 --> 10:25.037
I'm fine on my own.

10:25.836 --> 10:27.397
It's fine. I'm off duty anyway.

10:29.716 --> 10:30.197
Xu Yan.

10:33.197 --> 10:34.116
Yu Yiming?

10:34.716 --> 10:35.516
Long time no see.

10:41.356 --> 10:42.236
What happened?

10:44.077 --> 10:45.677
Nothing serious. Just a minor injury.

10:45.836 --> 10:46.957
If you're busy,

10:46.957 --> 10:47.677
I'm fine.

10:47.756 --> 10:48.596
You can go back.

10:50.596 --> 10:51.716
It's been a long time.

10:52.077 --> 10:52.876
How have you been?

10:53.636 --> 10:54.317
Working at?

10:57.356 --> 10:58.317
After graduation,

10:58.437 --> 10:59.756
I stayed in Jingzhou.

11:00.797 --> 11:01.437
That's good.

11:01.996 --> 11:02.876
I work here.

11:03.876 --> 11:04.797
An orthopedic doctor.

11:08.116 --> 11:09.116
Thank you for today.

11:09.636 --> 11:10.197
Of course.

11:16.957 --> 11:17.596
You got married?

11:20.596 --> 11:21.236
Yes, last month.

11:22.677 --> 11:23.716
Though it's a bit late,

11:24.476 --> 11:25.356
congratulations.

11:27.836 --> 11:29.037
Now that your sister's here,

11:29.077 --> 11:29.716
I'm relieved.

11:30.157 --> 11:31.077
Take your drugs.

11:31.756 --> 11:33.677
If anything, let me know.

11:39.157 --> 11:39.636
Bye.

12:00.996 --> 12:01.516
Let's go.

12:03.437 --> 12:04.557
Okay, let's go.

12:07.596 --> 12:08.437
Thanks for coming.

12:13.277 --> 12:14.636
My room is right across.

12:29.116 --> 12:30.116
Found a place,

12:31.756 --> 12:32.876
got a job too.

12:34.636 --> 12:36.437
Seems you're really staying in Jingzhou.

12:36.636 --> 12:37.996
Stop meddling in my affairs.

12:42.836 --> 12:44.917
Those two are my roommates' rooms.

12:51.797 --> 12:52.356
Move out.

12:53.917 --> 12:55.636
What nonsense are you saying?

12:55.797 --> 12:56.756
Your bedroom's small,

12:56.957 --> 12:58.157
with no private bathroom

12:58.756 --> 12:59.797
and barely any furniture.

13:01.917 --> 13:03.088
I'll find you a new place.

13:04.116 --> 13:05.516
Who asked you to do that?

13:06.197 --> 13:07.277
I'm not helping you.

13:08.516 --> 13:10.197
Since you're staying in Jingzhou,

13:10.677 --> 13:12.437
I don't need any trouble from you.

13:14.636 --> 13:15.596
If not for Yu Yiming,

13:15.636 --> 13:16.797
I wouldn't have called you.

13:17.157 --> 13:18.797
Even if I got hurt like today

13:18.836 --> 13:20.077
or die somewhere someday,

13:20.157 --> 13:22.356
I'd never blame you for it.

13:22.397 --> 13:22.876
Okay?

13:26.756 --> 13:27.356
What?

13:33.116 --> 13:34.516
The room right across.

13:34.557 --> 13:35.197
Empty it.

13:35.516 --> 13:36.037
Thanks.

13:37.356 --> 13:38.116
Why are you inside?

13:38.356 --> 13:38.756
No, no.

13:39.317 --> 13:39.876
What now?

13:43.437 --> 13:44.476
I said I'm not moving!

13:44.716 --> 13:45.957
Why dismantle my place?

13:47.197 --> 13:48.157
You have two options.

13:48.636 --> 13:49.077
First,

13:49.596 --> 13:51.317
have your parents
take you home to recover.

13:51.557 --> 13:52.756
Second, obey me.

13:53.876 --> 13:55.356
Who's the elder sister here?

13:55.516 --> 13:57.236
Don't think your success makes you king.

13:57.397 --> 13:58.476
Don't touch my things!

13:58.636 --> 13:59.476
Hands off my stuff!

14:00.236 --> 14:00.836
Keep this up,

14:00.876 --> 14:01.917
and I'll call the police.

14:01.957 --> 14:03.236
Trespassing! You know that?

14:04.077 --> 14:04.756
Make them leave.

14:09.037 --> 14:10.236
Don't be ungrateful.

14:11.516 --> 14:13.157
When we were kids,

14:14.077 --> 14:15.077
you helped me fight.

14:15.636 --> 14:16.636
I'm repaying the favor.

14:18.037 --> 14:20.077
You remembered such a small matter?

14:20.636 --> 14:21.516
It's fine. Not needed.

14:21.636 --> 14:22.596
I don't need that.

14:22.716 --> 14:23.797
But I must return it

14:24.236 --> 14:26.197
so that I can feel no debts between us.

14:26.797 --> 14:27.317
I won't move.

14:28.797 --> 14:29.636
You won't move?

14:29.836 --> 14:30.277
No.

14:32.596 --> 14:33.157
Fine.

14:34.356 --> 14:35.317
I forgot to tell you.

14:35.677 --> 14:37.557
The new apartment's neighbor
is Yu Yiming.

14:38.116 --> 14:39.197
No need to move, guys.

14:39.476 --> 14:40.077
Move! Move!

14:40.116 --> 14:40.797
I must move!

14:40.957 --> 14:42.197
Sorry about earlier.

14:42.356 --> 14:43.476
Let me help you with that.

14:43.636 --> 14:44.557
Here, I'll pack this.

14:46.917 --> 14:47.636
Who is it?

15:03.677 --> 15:04.236
Good morning.

15:04.996 --> 15:05.356
Morning.

15:07.917 --> 15:08.317
Qiao Lin.

15:09.596 --> 15:09.957
Qiao Lin?

15:12.116 --> 15:12.756
You're injured.

15:12.996 --> 15:13.596
Your breakfast.

15:15.516 --> 15:16.037
Thanks.

15:18.516 --> 15:20.077
Have... you eaten? Join me?

15:20.236 --> 15:20.797
I already ate.

15:21.317 --> 15:21.636
Oh.

15:21.996 --> 15:23.356
I'll send you the cafeteria menu.

15:23.596 --> 15:24.836
You can give me a lunch order.

15:25.797 --> 15:26.836
- Leaving.
- Bye.

15:28.476 --> 15:28.996
Bye.

15:37.776 --> 15:40.689
(Jingzhou Yuekang Hospital
Staff Cafeteria Weekly Menu)

16:00.756 --> 16:01.797
Dad, Mom.

16:02.876 --> 16:03.557
What's wrong?

16:05.397 --> 16:06.957
It's so late. Why haven't you cooked?

16:07.756 --> 16:08.677
Do you know

16:09.596 --> 16:11.636
our whole family
got tricked by that Qiao?

16:14.037 --> 16:14.836
How?

16:15.277 --> 16:17.516
I ran into Ms. Chen today on the road.

16:17.996 --> 16:19.836
She used to work with Wang Yazhen.

16:19.876 --> 16:20.397
Remember her?

16:21.516 --> 16:23.157
Qiao Jianbin and Wang Yazhen

16:23.437 --> 16:25.317
bought a storefront on Commercial Street

16:25.397 --> 16:26.077
for a barbershop.

16:26.236 --> 16:27.516
Already paid the down payment.

16:28.037 --> 16:28.677
Think about it.

16:28.917 --> 16:29.957
Where is the money from?

16:30.197 --> 16:31.277
How would I know?

16:31.677 --> 16:33.157
Are you stupid?

16:34.157 --> 16:35.476
Their family is dirt poor.

16:35.836 --> 16:36.917
How could they afford this?

16:37.596 --> 16:39.797
Must've used our bride price money!

16:40.037 --> 16:40.957
Never thought the girl

16:41.077 --> 16:42.836
who acts so carelessly

16:43.317 --> 16:45.197
would be so shrewd with money.

16:45.516 --> 16:47.116
Good thing you didn't marry her!

16:48.516 --> 16:49.596
Listen, son.

16:50.157 --> 16:52.077
We need to get that money back.

16:52.596 --> 16:55.077
We can't lose face and money!

16:59.472 --> 17:00.472
(Qiao Lin, my parents want
the bride price back.)

17:00.472 --> 17:01.332
(But don't worry, I don't agree.)

17:01.332 --> 17:02.042
(Because I still love you.)

17:02.042 --> 17:02.542
(I won't hold this against you.)

17:02.542 --> 17:03.536
(I'll come to Jingzhou tomorrow.
Let's meet up.)

17:07.024 --> 17:08.240
(The message was sent
but rejected by the recipient.)

17:10.877 --> 17:11.917
She blocked me.

17:17.556 --> 17:19.877
Sorry, the number you dialed

17:19.917 --> 17:21.316
is unavailable now.

17:21.357 --> 17:22.476
Please try again later.

17:23.756 --> 17:25.437
Phone's blocked too.

17:26.036 --> 17:26.756
Qiao Lin.

17:27.597 --> 17:28.516
This is too much.

17:43.597 --> 17:44.036
Hello.

17:44.157 --> 17:45.637
- Hello.
- I'm looking for

17:45.756 --> 17:47.476
the host of Family Feast,

17:47.597 --> 17:48.397
named Qiao Yan.

17:49.796 --> 17:51.076
She goes by Xu Yan now.

17:51.197 --> 17:52.637
Do you have an appointment, sir?

17:53.316 --> 17:53.837
No.

17:54.597 --> 17:55.157
I'm sorry.

17:55.236 --> 17:56.837
No visitors without appointments.

17:59.197 --> 18:01.597
Could you call her to come meet me?

18:01.996 --> 18:03.716
Her brother-in-law Lin Tao is here.

18:04.756 --> 18:06.917
You can call her to come get you.

18:12.397 --> 18:13.076
Thanks then.

18:13.236 --> 18:14.197
You're welcome, sir.

18:21.516 --> 18:22.117
Sir.

18:22.877 --> 18:24.076
Who are you looking for?

18:25.437 --> 18:25.756
Uh...

18:25.756 --> 18:27.877
I'm looking for Xu Yan,
the host of Family Feast.

18:28.397 --> 18:29.437
Do you have a pass?

18:32.677 --> 18:33.716
No entry without a pass.

18:34.236 --> 18:34.957
Please leave now.

18:34.996 --> 18:35.677
Get out of there.

18:36.157 --> 18:37.476
No, I'll just be a moment.

18:37.556 --> 18:38.316
Sir, please.

18:38.357 --> 18:39.117
Leave immediately.

18:47.276 --> 18:49.437
Thank you so much, Yiming.

18:51.877 --> 18:53.117
You're very welcome.

18:53.917 --> 18:55.276
We're high school classmates

18:55.397 --> 18:56.157
and folks at home.

18:56.597 --> 18:57.357
In Jingzhou,

18:57.397 --> 18:58.677
we should help each other.

18:59.276 --> 18:59.996
Besides,

19:01.076 --> 19:02.236
Qiao Lin is my patient.

19:04.796 --> 19:05.397
From now on,

19:05.516 --> 19:06.957
if Qiao Lin needs anything

19:06.996 --> 19:08.197
or gets in trouble,

19:08.837 --> 19:10.556
please contact me directly.

19:12.516 --> 19:12.996
No problem.

19:16.117 --> 19:17.036
You know,

19:17.996 --> 19:19.637
Qiao Lin's family and I

19:19.677 --> 19:20.716
are always like this.

19:22.476 --> 19:23.236
Thank you.

19:24.877 --> 19:25.917
Actually, I can tell

19:26.637 --> 19:28.316
you care deeply about your sister.

19:29.677 --> 19:32.236
Why don't you just sit down and talk?

19:32.516 --> 19:33.556
I like it this way.

19:34.157 --> 19:35.796
We have our own lives,

19:36.516 --> 19:37.637
keeping a distance,

19:38.316 --> 19:39.157
and being at peace.

19:39.637 --> 19:40.236
It's great.

19:49.437 --> 19:50.756
Hey, Lin Tao.

19:51.276 --> 19:51.837
Mr. Qiao,

19:54.197 --> 19:57.117
do you have Qiao Yan's number?

19:57.637 --> 19:58.236
Yan?

19:59.236 --> 20:00.476
Do you need to contact her?

20:02.716 --> 20:03.397
Yeah.

20:04.677 --> 20:06.516
Alright, I'll look for it.

20:13.756 --> 20:14.236
Sir,

20:14.837 --> 20:15.597
don't bother.

20:16.276 --> 20:16.957
I got it.

20:17.996 --> 20:18.556
I know

20:19.397 --> 20:21.076
you want Qiao Lin and me to be close.

20:23.316 --> 20:24.597
But it's been too long.

20:25.157 --> 20:26.036
There's no need.

20:26.796 --> 20:28.157
Qiao Lin just broke up

20:28.236 --> 20:29.437
and lives alone now.

20:30.556 --> 20:31.476
With you next door,

20:31.516 --> 20:32.556
I feel more at ease.

20:33.756 --> 20:35.597
But please do look after her for me.

20:36.316 --> 20:37.157
Don't worry.

20:37.677 --> 20:38.476
It's appropriate

20:38.837 --> 20:40.117
for me to take care of her.

20:40.597 --> 20:41.036
Thank you.

20:41.756 --> 20:42.276
Qiao Yan.

20:45.796 --> 20:47.076
Why ask him to do that?

20:47.917 --> 20:48.516
Who is he?

20:55.556 --> 20:56.117
Who is he?

20:56.637 --> 20:57.837
Lin Tao, calm down.

20:58.197 --> 21:00.076
Qiao Lin and I
went to high school with him.

21:00.117 --> 21:00.677
That's all.

21:00.996 --> 21:01.476
Hello.

21:02.837 --> 21:03.556
I'm Yu Yiming.

21:04.637 --> 21:05.597
High school classmates?

21:06.476 --> 21:08.756
Then why let Qiao Lin
move next door to him?

21:10.036 --> 21:12.076
I know why Qiao Lin
called off our engagement.

21:12.316 --> 21:13.837
You schemed it, didn't you?

21:13.837 --> 21:14.597
What did I do?

21:16.276 --> 21:16.837
Take this out.

21:16.877 --> 21:18.157
If you hadn't tricked Qiao Lin,

21:18.597 --> 21:19.516
why would she come here

21:19.756 --> 21:20.837
and get close to him?

21:21.117 --> 21:22.397
Qiao Yan, what's wrong with you?

21:22.437 --> 21:23.756
This is a public place.

21:26.157 --> 21:28.476
Go outside, and we'll talk.

21:28.796 --> 21:29.197
No.

21:29.476 --> 21:29.877
Qiao Yan.

21:30.397 --> 21:31.437
What's wrong with you?

21:31.957 --> 21:33.157
Wait, hold on a second.

21:36.197 --> 21:36.677
Wait.

21:38.197 --> 21:39.157
You pushed me!

21:39.597 --> 21:41.716
You seduced my fiancﾃｩe,
and now you're pushing me?

21:41.917 --> 21:42.437
Qiao Yan.

21:42.837 --> 21:44.316
You helped your sister cheat.

21:44.597 --> 21:46.117
You two are disgusting.

21:46.157 --> 21:47.236
Watch your mouth.

21:47.397 --> 21:47.996
Go outside.

21:48.197 --> 21:48.677
No.

21:48.996 --> 21:50.316
Say it here.

21:50.556 --> 21:51.756
Where is Qiao Lin really?

21:51.996 --> 21:52.957
Get her here

21:53.117 --> 21:54.437
and explain everything.

21:54.637 --> 21:56.397
I want every detail laid out clearly.

21:56.437 --> 21:57.316
I know where she is.

21:59.397 --> 22:00.197
I'll take you there.

22:05.276 --> 22:05.796
Go ahead.

22:16.556 --> 22:17.276
No lying, huh?

22:20.157 --> 22:20.877
What happened?

22:20.877 --> 22:21.316
Sorry.

22:21.716 --> 22:22.276
I'm not sure.

22:22.476 --> 22:23.476
Ask this gentleman.

22:23.917 --> 22:25.236
Sorry, are your clothes alright?

22:25.597 --> 22:26.316
Yeah, thank you.

22:26.877 --> 22:27.516
Hey, handsome.

22:28.597 --> 22:29.837
What happened here earlier?

22:30.716 --> 22:31.316
You are...

22:31.796 --> 22:33.197
I'm Xu Yan's colleague.

22:33.357 --> 22:35.437
I saw a man leave with her just now.

22:35.476 --> 22:36.276
Are they...

22:37.236 --> 22:37.996
I don't know them.

22:38.236 --> 22:39.637
They bumped into me just now.

22:40.036 --> 22:40.637
Sorry.

22:48.597 --> 22:49.917
You teamed up

22:49.957 --> 22:51.197
to help her cheat on me, huh?

22:51.837 --> 22:53.597
This matter won't be
swept under the rug.

22:53.837 --> 22:55.637
What I just said simply

22:57.036 --> 22:59.076
went through one ear
and out the other, right?

22:59.597 --> 23:00.556
Get her here

23:01.397 --> 23:02.357
to explain it to me.

23:02.556 --> 23:04.276
She'll swear that she has

23:04.316 --> 23:05.716
no romance with that Yu.

23:05.796 --> 23:06.516
You're pathetic.

23:06.837 --> 23:07.556
Scared, huh?

23:08.837 --> 23:09.996
Afraid she'll slip up.

23:10.597 --> 23:12.036
Qiao Yan, you never speak the truth.

23:18.556 --> 23:19.157
I'm leaving.

23:19.837 --> 23:21.197
Two final things for you.

23:21.556 --> 23:22.036
First,

23:23.276 --> 23:24.796
you've broken up with Qiao Lin.

23:25.877 --> 23:27.197
You have no connection anymore.

23:27.276 --> 23:28.036
- I...
- Second,

23:28.597 --> 23:30.917
I forbid you from meddling in
her current life.

23:32.357 --> 23:33.556
I'm done. Understood?

23:36.796 --> 23:37.397
Firstly,

23:38.197 --> 23:39.957
the breakup was her unilateral decision.

23:40.197 --> 23:40.957
I never agreed.

23:41.316 --> 23:42.677
How can we have no connection?

23:43.076 --> 23:44.076
She's my fiancﾃｩe!

23:44.236 --> 23:46.076
Your family accepted the bride price!

23:49.917 --> 23:50.516
How much?

23:51.076 --> 23:51.597
I'll pay.

23:55.556 --> 23:56.877
This isn't about money!

23:56.957 --> 23:58.276
I want her! Her!

23:59.276 --> 23:59.957
I don't know.

24:02.236 --> 24:02.756
Fine.

24:04.197 --> 24:04.877
Won't talk?

24:05.756 --> 24:06.837
Then I'll come every day.

24:07.076 --> 24:08.476
I'll demand her at your workplace.

24:08.597 --> 24:09.796
Hound your in-laws for her.

24:10.397 --> 24:11.476
Didn't you marry well?

24:11.917 --> 24:12.957
I'll show them what kind

24:13.076 --> 24:13.996
of shameless things

24:14.036 --> 24:15.696
you've been doing behind their backs.

24:25.437 --> 24:26.076
Suit yourself.

24:36.437 --> 24:36.996
Coming.

24:45.437 --> 24:45.917
I'll get it.

24:57.437 --> 24:58.197
Good grief!

24:59.996 --> 25:02.197
He's completely insane!

25:03.877 --> 25:05.357
Always looked down on me,

25:05.716 --> 25:08.076
saying I couldn't help his career,

25:08.476 --> 25:10.197
now falsely accusing me of cheating!

25:10.276 --> 25:10.716
Well,

25:10.957 --> 25:11.476
such madness!

25:11.728 --> 25:12.516
I'm so pissed off!

25:15.236 --> 25:16.276
What will you do?

25:18.316 --> 25:19.957
He wants me to confront him directly?

25:20.157 --> 25:20.516
Fine.

25:20.756 --> 25:21.597
Talk to him directly.

25:21.716 --> 25:22.716
Watch me beat him hard!

25:27.197 --> 25:28.236
I won't recommend that.

25:29.357 --> 25:31.440
It's unnecessary for you
to drain yourself like this.

25:32.197 --> 25:33.516
Since you broke up,

25:33.877 --> 25:35.796
make a clean break from the past.

25:37.197 --> 25:38.117
I talked with Lin Tao.

25:38.917 --> 25:39.796
What he cares about

25:40.157 --> 25:42.076
is your emotional loyalty to him.

25:42.197 --> 25:45.316
But his parents only
care about the money.

25:47.076 --> 25:48.516
Don't worry about the money.

25:48.917 --> 25:49.996
I'll handle it for you.

25:50.437 --> 25:51.197
This way,

25:51.796 --> 25:53.197
even if he causes trouble here,

25:53.837 --> 25:55.036
his parents will stop him.

25:57.877 --> 25:59.437
I don't need your help with this.

25:59.556 --> 26:00.516
I'll handle it myself.

26:00.677 --> 26:01.276
How exactly?

26:03.316 --> 26:04.276
When will you handle it?

26:05.597 --> 26:06.476
With what?

26:07.236 --> 26:07.677
I...

26:17.917 --> 26:19.877
By the time you got the money,

26:20.677 --> 26:21.957
Lin Tao would have made this

26:21.996 --> 26:23.076
public knowledge by then.

26:23.996 --> 26:25.397
By then, my workplace,

26:25.677 --> 26:26.316
the Shen family,

26:26.597 --> 26:27.796
and everyone else would know.

26:30.197 --> 26:30.556
I...

26:31.236 --> 26:31.837
I thought

26:31.837 --> 26:33.476
you were considering my interests.

26:33.837 --> 26:36.080
Turns out you're just afraid
your lies will be exposed.

26:40.197 --> 26:40.716
Yes.

26:43.677 --> 26:44.957
I did it for myself.

26:48.157 --> 26:49.157
Because since childhood,

26:49.197 --> 26:50.877
I've had to learn to prioritize myself.

26:50.917 --> 26:52.036
I'm not you.

26:55.796 --> 26:57.556
I don't need you causing
more trouble for me.

26:58.516 --> 27:00.036
If money can solve it,

27:00.197 --> 27:01.076
I'll handle it.

27:01.877 --> 27:03.824
Fine. I won't cause you trouble.

27:05.157 --> 27:06.357
Consider this money a loan.

27:06.516 --> 27:08.197
The rent for the apartment
is also a loan.

27:08.236 --> 27:09.796
I'll pay you back in installments.

27:10.236 --> 27:10.877
Qiao Lin.

27:11.276 --> 27:11.756
What?

27:11.888 --> 27:13.516
What do you ever do
besides acting tough?

27:13.516 --> 27:14.036
I don't.

27:14.236 --> 27:15.397
- Look at your arm!
- I...

27:43.837 --> 27:45.157
Who is this Lin Tao?

27:46.117 --> 27:47.117
Claims to be your wife's

27:47.157 --> 27:48.197
cousin's fiancﾃｩ.

27:50.677 --> 27:53.556
Investigate his employment status
and social connections.

27:54.516 --> 27:54.996
Understood.

28:02.597 --> 28:04.197
Son, all the money's been transferred.

28:04.437 --> 28:06.637
If there's nothing in Jingzhou,
come home immediately.

28:07.076 --> 28:09.516
I'm not going back.
I need to stay here a few more days.

28:10.597 --> 28:11.556
Quit while you're ahead.

28:12.316 --> 28:14.117
Her sister has quite the influence.

28:14.157 --> 28:15.076
Don't make enemies.

28:15.677 --> 28:16.157
Exactly.

28:16.236 --> 28:16.716
Mom, Dad,

28:17.157 --> 28:18.117
if I don't find out

28:18.157 --> 28:19.917
whether Qiao Lin called off the wedding

28:19.917 --> 28:20.957
because she has an affair,

28:20.957 --> 28:21.957
I'm never going back!

28:22.677 --> 28:23.280
I'll hang up.

28:24.837 --> 28:25.397
Lin Tao,

28:26.096 --> 28:27.276
the reason I called you here

28:27.276 --> 28:29.397
is to inform you the leadership

28:29.516 --> 28:30.957
values your development highly.

28:31.516 --> 28:32.397
Keep working hard.

28:32.677 --> 28:33.197
Understood?

28:33.556 --> 28:34.117
Sir,

28:35.516 --> 28:38.597
you dragged me back
from Jingzhou for this?

28:41.197 --> 28:42.796
Sir, when I asked for leave,

28:42.796 --> 28:44.397
I explained in Jingzhou,

28:44.597 --> 28:45.877
I have urgent family matters.

28:45.996 --> 28:46.917
Why make me...?

28:46.957 --> 28:48.957
Isn't this about
the account reconciliation?

28:49.157 --> 28:50.276
We need you.

28:52.516 --> 28:52.957
Well,

28:54.157 --> 28:56.076
account reconciliation
isn't my responsibility.

28:56.276 --> 28:58.157
It's the emphasis
on your career development.

28:58.637 --> 28:59.556
Enough. Stop arguing.

29:00.437 --> 29:01.837
Your leave request is denied.

29:02.316 --> 29:03.197
You're staying here.

29:03.597 --> 29:04.756
Why?

29:07.476 --> 29:08.476
To be honest,

29:08.877 --> 29:11.197
this leave request wasn't denied by me.

29:12.236 --> 29:13.556
Mr. Zhou rejected it.

29:14.597 --> 29:15.276
Mr. Zhou?

29:16.877 --> 29:17.837
How did my leave request

29:17.917 --> 29:18.996
reach the executive level?

29:19.036 --> 29:20.076
I don't know.

29:20.397 --> 29:21.877
Mr. Zhou called me this morning

29:21.957 --> 29:22.677
asking about you.

29:23.117 --> 29:24.357
I said you'd taken leave.

29:25.357 --> 29:27.316
Leadership showed great concern,

29:27.637 --> 29:29.637
telling me to recall you immediately.

29:30.197 --> 29:31.197
They praised you

29:31.516 --> 29:33.516
and told me to assign you
more responsibilities.

29:40.117 --> 29:40.637
Lin Tao,

29:41.756 --> 29:42.957
tell me the truth.

29:43.397 --> 29:45.756
What's your relationship with Mr. Zhou?

29:46.756 --> 29:47.796
Nothing's going on.

29:47.996 --> 29:48.877
Nothing?

29:49.197 --> 29:50.796
But he specifically inquired about you.

29:52.837 --> 29:53.397
Tao,

29:54.036 --> 29:55.197
stop pretending with me.

29:56.716 --> 29:57.957
The boss cares a lot about you.

29:58.276 --> 30:00.117
You'll have a bright future ahead.

30:01.437 --> 30:01.996
From now on,

30:01.996 --> 30:03.312
don't take unnecessary leaves.

30:03.312 --> 30:04.677
It looks bad for your reputation.

30:05.677 --> 30:07.036
Alright. Get back to work.

30:07.637 --> 30:08.357
Go on.

30:18.036 --> 30:18.957
Honey, are you ready?

30:19.117 --> 30:20.117
Almost there.

30:20.556 --> 30:21.837
I'll count down from five.

30:22.276 --> 30:22.796
Don't!

30:22.796 --> 30:23.316
Five.

30:23.677 --> 30:24.157
No counting.

30:24.157 --> 30:24.677
Four.

30:24.677 --> 30:25.397
Stop counting.

30:25.397 --> 30:25.957
Three.

30:26.197 --> 30:26.637
Two.

30:26.957 --> 30:27.397
One.

30:29.397 --> 30:29.837
Done.

30:31.076 --> 30:32.516
You cheated!

30:34.476 --> 30:36.197
You didn't even finish the count.

30:37.076 --> 30:38.276
What kind of

30:39.996 --> 30:40.917
dish

30:42.677 --> 30:43.917
is this?

30:44.236 --> 30:45.076
Isn't it obvious?

30:45.360 --> 30:46.608
Shrimp-stuffed potato chips.

30:48.036 --> 30:49.677
Why such a literal name?

30:50.637 --> 30:51.877
They're delicious, really.

30:51.996 --> 30:52.437
Try one.

30:54.157 --> 30:54.637
Well?

30:56.276 --> 30:56.756
Good?

30:57.437 --> 30:57.957
As expected,

30:59.157 --> 31:00.556
the chips taste like chips.

31:01.597 --> 31:03.357
The shrimp tastes like shrimp.

31:04.716 --> 31:05.756
Say it seriously.

31:06.197 --> 31:08.236
This will be the featured dish
in my next episode.

31:08.637 --> 31:09.712
It's really that bad?

31:11.516 --> 31:12.397
That's my fault.

31:12.996 --> 31:14.036
Let me try another piece.

31:15.632 --> 31:18.464
笙ｪTo reignite笙ｪ

31:18.637 --> 31:19.197
Different now.

31:20.637 --> 31:21.837
The chips carry shrimp flavor.

31:22.637 --> 31:24.316
The shrimp tastes potatoey.

31:25.397 --> 31:26.756
Just like you and me.

31:27.076 --> 31:28.996
You carry traces of me.
I carry traces of you.

31:28.996 --> 31:29.917
Mixed together.

31:30.117 --> 31:30.556
Amazing.

31:31.117 --> 31:31.437
Okay.

31:31.597 --> 31:32.197
Alright.

31:32.357 --> 31:33.397
Let me taste your dish.

31:35.357 --> 31:35.917
Codfish.

31:36.556 --> 31:37.117
Have a bite.

31:37.157 --> 31:37.756
Wait.

31:37.996 --> 31:39.236
This isn't ordinary cod.

31:39.316 --> 31:39.756
What is it?

31:40.357 --> 31:42.357
It's Shen-family secret recipe cod.

31:42.397 --> 31:43.316
Extraordinary cod.

31:43.516 --> 31:43.996
Taste it.

31:47.036 --> 31:48.556
Let me name this cod dish. Okay?

31:48.837 --> 31:49.157
Fine.

31:49.556 --> 31:50.117
We'll call it

31:51.197 --> 31:52.516
Charcoal in Snowstorm?

31:52.996 --> 31:53.957
It's completely charred.

31:56.036 --> 31:56.996
That's a terrible pun.

31:57.476 --> 31:58.316
Here, try it.

31:58.597 --> 31:58.917
Fine.

32:05.556 --> 32:08.316
Perfectly preserves
the cod's natural fishiness.

32:08.476 --> 32:09.076
Very good.

32:24.036 --> 32:25.357
(Given Lin Tao's personality,)

32:26.157 --> 32:27.677
(I thought he'd keep pressing.)

32:28.877 --> 32:30.036
(But unexpectedly,)

32:30.796 --> 32:31.996
(he suddenly vanished.)

32:44.036 --> 32:45.996
I contacted Mr. Huang's office.

32:46.437 --> 32:49.236
They said he is going abroad
for inspection.

32:49.397 --> 32:50.437
His schedule's packed.

32:50.917 --> 32:52.076
Can't arrange a meeting now.

32:53.236 --> 32:54.316
I also heard...

32:54.837 --> 32:55.516
Heard what?

32:59.316 --> 33:00.157
Out with it.

33:00.437 --> 33:00.837
Speak.

33:01.996 --> 33:03.516
Mr. Huang calls you the heir apparent.

33:10.677 --> 33:12.197
He knows my funding's limited.

33:13.008 --> 33:14.256
I have insufficient influence.

33:14.357 --> 33:15.437
He is clearly avoiding me.

33:15.796 --> 33:17.036
What's our next step?

33:17.677 --> 33:19.036
Keep pursuing him?

33:19.996 --> 33:21.877
Proceed as planned.

33:22.476 --> 33:24.516
Thoroughly study
his company's structure.

33:24.637 --> 33:25.157
Okay.

33:27.856 --> 33:30.110
(Plot Plan)

33:32.796 --> 33:33.556
In short,

33:33.756 --> 33:35.716
we shouldn't rush on this land deal.

33:35.917 --> 33:37.197
Listen to your father.

33:38.597 --> 33:39.716
If he doesn't approve,

33:39.996 --> 33:42.117
Mr. Huang from Shouke
won't risk partnering with you.

33:42.117 --> 33:42.556
Right?

33:44.917 --> 33:45.316
Alright.

33:45.637 --> 33:46.437
Don't overthink it.

33:46.796 --> 33:47.716
He's your father.

33:48.197 --> 33:49.397
Every decision he makes

33:49.476 --> 33:50.516
is for your benefit.

33:50.716 --> 33:52.917
Tonight he's hosting Shifeng people
for dinner at home.

33:53.597 --> 33:55.197
Don't let your emotions show.

33:57.796 --> 33:58.512
Give us a smile.

33:59.316 --> 33:59.837
Got it.

34:03.877 --> 34:04.357
Mom.

34:04.476 --> 34:05.036
Haoming.

34:05.236 --> 34:06.036
Have some fruits.

34:06.637 --> 34:07.516
You're back.

34:10.996 --> 34:13.116
You two chat first.
I'll call you when dinner's ready.

34:13.317 --> 34:13.757
Alright.

34:17.676 --> 34:18.076
Sit.

34:20.797 --> 34:22.036
What were you talking with Mom?

34:23.556 --> 34:24.336
Nothing important.

34:24.837 --> 34:25.996
Just some minor work stuff.

34:28.917 --> 34:29.277
Good boy.

34:29.596 --> 34:30.277
Have some water.

34:30.437 --> 34:31.036
Pass me Bu.

34:31.917 --> 34:32.516
Bu!

34:33.196 --> 34:33.957
Let's go, Bu!

34:37.437 --> 34:38.116
Can you sit?

34:38.917 --> 34:39.516
Can you sit?

34:40.156 --> 34:40.516
Sit.

34:41.277 --> 34:41.636
Sit.

34:42.757 --> 34:43.312
Shake hands.

34:43.877 --> 34:44.797
Shake hands.

34:46.397 --> 34:46.797
Come on.

34:47.556 --> 34:48.556
Come on, shake hands.

34:50.516 --> 34:51.277
Such a good boy.

35:09.196 --> 35:10.128
Where are we going?

35:11.116 --> 35:12.036
You'll see soon.

35:13.156 --> 35:13.516
Let's go.

35:19.996 --> 35:20.797
You found it.

35:21.797 --> 35:23.317
I stumbled upon it accidentally.

35:24.196 --> 35:25.156
I asked Hui.

35:25.476 --> 35:27.156
She said you made this as a child.

35:28.476 --> 35:28.996
Yeah.

35:30.116 --> 35:31.516
This thing's pretty old.

35:31.996 --> 35:33.556
When I was in elementary school,

35:34.357 --> 35:36.277
my dad wanted to renovate this villa.

35:36.757 --> 35:38.996
They made this opening
and planned to fix it,

35:39.476 --> 35:40.277
but I stopped them.

35:40.957 --> 35:42.076
Then I made this instead.

35:48.717 --> 35:50.757
How did you have such
good craftsmanship as a child?

35:53.676 --> 35:54.636
A little bear,

35:57.516 --> 35:58.556
a small window.

36:00.717 --> 36:02.237
It's gazing outside,

36:02.837 --> 36:03.877
hiding here,

36:05.397 --> 36:06.596
looking so lonely.

36:07.837 --> 36:09.277
Maybe it wants

36:09.397 --> 36:11.196
to hide all the disappointments
and sadness

36:11.237 --> 36:12.476
here inside.

36:13.317 --> 36:14.877
Stay hidden and slowly process them,

36:15.636 --> 36:17.957
only showing the happy side to others.

36:20.717 --> 36:21.797
That's why I...

36:25.636 --> 36:27.036
I added this little lamp,

36:30.397 --> 36:31.237
hoping

36:32.957 --> 36:35.636
it could chase away
those gloomy feelings

36:37.277 --> 36:38.237
and end its loneliness.

36:46.556 --> 36:47.357
Haoming,

36:51.237 --> 36:52.476
I know you care about me,

36:54.516 --> 36:55.676
but I don't need you

36:56.996 --> 36:59.437
to shield me from all your troubles

36:59.556 --> 37:00.596
and worries.

37:02.516 --> 37:04.036
I want to share your burdens

37:04.076 --> 37:05.397
and anxieties with you.

37:08.516 --> 37:09.357
Your happiness

37:10.636 --> 37:11.797
makes me happier.

37:26.516 --> 37:27.196
Thank you.

37:48.944 --> 37:52.184
(Jingzhou Conrad Hotel)

37:53.596 --> 37:55.636
Mr. Huang from Shouke Real Estate

37:57.757 --> 37:59.196
is notoriously difficult.

37:59.476 --> 38:02.156
I'm quite social-savvy,

38:02.317 --> 38:03.437
but dealing with him

38:03.797 --> 38:05.156
is like hitting a brick wall.

38:05.797 --> 38:07.196
He's such an eccentric person.

38:09.277 --> 38:10.636
If he's eccentric,

38:12.556 --> 38:14.317
there must be some special backstory.

38:15.036 --> 38:16.917
That's why you're smart, Miss Xu.

38:17.717 --> 38:18.797
My husband mentioned

38:19.277 --> 38:21.808
that Mr. Huang has an extraordinary
relationship with his wife.

38:22.516 --> 38:23.676
In their circle,

38:23.996 --> 38:25.676
he's known for being a devoted husband.

38:26.036 --> 38:26.636
Later,

38:26.717 --> 38:28.156
his wife fell seriously ill.

38:28.556 --> 38:30.476
Mr. Huang abandoned
all business affairs.

38:30.917 --> 38:31.917
He accompanied his wife,

38:31.917 --> 38:33.957
seeking medical help
both domestically and abroad.

38:34.556 --> 38:35.116
In the end,

38:35.357 --> 38:37.437
his wife still passed away.

38:38.317 --> 38:39.877
Mr. Huang was devastated.

38:40.196 --> 38:41.717
His temperament changed.

38:43.277 --> 38:44.397
He never remarried.

38:45.556 --> 38:47.237
From what you say,

38:48.437 --> 38:49.957
Mr. Huang seems decent.

38:50.357 --> 38:51.357
He has good character.

38:52.116 --> 38:52.837
Meiling,

38:53.877 --> 38:54.996
do you know

38:55.156 --> 38:56.516
if he has any living relatives?

38:57.156 --> 38:57.996
Even extended family?

38:58.196 --> 38:59.437
There's hardly anyone left.

39:00.076 --> 39:01.516
The couple never had children.

39:02.480 --> 39:03.877
His mother-in-law is still alive.

39:04.277 --> 39:05.636
I've heard all these years

39:05.676 --> 39:07.996
he's been caring for her diligently.

39:08.196 --> 39:09.717
He wants to be her caretaker for life.

39:09.957 --> 39:12.277
But the old lady is stubborn.

39:12.757 --> 39:14.076
She moved to a nursing home.

39:14.437 --> 39:16.476
Mr. Huang couldn't change her mind,

39:16.837 --> 39:18.156
so he relented.

39:22.437 --> 39:23.757
In these business circles,

39:24.757 --> 39:26.476
is there anything you don't know?

39:26.917 --> 39:27.596
Not much.

39:34.996 --> 39:35.717
Miss Xu,

39:36.076 --> 39:37.317
thank you so much

39:37.476 --> 39:39.476
for donating these supplies
to our nursing home.

39:39.996 --> 39:40.516
Ms. Han,

39:41.076 --> 39:43.556
they're just daily necessities.
No need for formalities.

39:44.596 --> 39:45.277
Actually,

39:45.397 --> 39:47.036
I should be thanking you

39:47.636 --> 39:50.116
for letting us contribute.

39:50.397 --> 39:51.156
It's not easy.

39:56.357 --> 39:56.996
By the way,

39:57.676 --> 39:59.076
do you have a resident here

39:59.237 --> 40:00.717
named Yu Shufen?

40:01.156 --> 40:01.837
Yu Shufen?

40:02.317 --> 40:03.036
You know her?

40:03.676 --> 40:05.392
She's someone
my husband respected deeply.

40:05.757 --> 40:07.156
I'd like to visit her.

40:09.317 --> 40:10.036
Well...

40:12.036 --> 40:12.757
Is there an issue?

40:13.676 --> 40:14.797
Not really.

40:15.237 --> 40:16.237
I just think

40:16.596 --> 40:17.877
your visit might be...

40:23.317 --> 40:23.957
Get out!

40:24.357 --> 40:25.156
Get away from me!

40:25.556 --> 40:26.996
Don't blame me!

40:27.636 --> 40:28.596
It's your own fault!

40:28.676 --> 40:29.476
You thief!

40:29.516 --> 40:30.196
Shameless!

40:30.317 --> 40:31.476
I told you to leave!

40:31.757 --> 40:32.237
You...

40:32.516 --> 40:33.516
I've said everything!

40:33.596 --> 40:34.277
Not leaving?

40:34.877 --> 40:35.917
Stop following me!

40:36.277 --> 40:37.277
Utterly shameless!

40:37.397 --> 40:38.476
So thick-skinned!

40:38.877 --> 40:40.397
How dare you steal from me!

40:40.717 --> 40:41.516
Back off!

40:42.036 --> 40:42.877
I'll beat you up!

40:43.156 --> 40:44.156
Utterly shameless!

40:44.317 --> 40:45.797
What's left to steal?

40:46.476 --> 40:47.397
You're shameless!

40:47.437 --> 40:48.476
Stop dodging!

40:48.757 --> 40:50.237
Stop dodging!

40:50.556 --> 40:51.516
Miss Xu,

40:51.596 --> 40:52.877
this is Yu Shufen.

40:53.556 --> 40:54.596
Alzheimer's disease,

40:55.196 --> 40:56.476
mid-to-late stage.

40:57.397 --> 40:58.596
As you know,

40:59.357 --> 41:00.596
for patients like this,

41:01.036 --> 41:03.917
we can only provide

41:03.917 --> 41:05.036
a comfortable environment.

41:05.596 --> 41:08.437
Caregivers guide them through

41:09.397 --> 41:11.036
Baduanjin exercises

41:11.397 --> 41:12.357
and finger exercises.

41:12.917 --> 41:16.076
This helps slow
the disease's progression.

41:17.237 --> 41:17.957
I said

41:19.357 --> 41:20.036
leave!

41:23.116 --> 41:23.917
Meatballs!

41:40.116 --> 41:44.596
One, two, three, four...

41:45.397 --> 41:47.556
What's Madam Yu holding?

41:48.596 --> 41:49.957
Counting vegetable balls.

41:50.917 --> 41:51.837
Vegetable balls.

41:59.837 --> 42:00.917
Grandma!

42:00.957 --> 42:02.156
Are the vegetable balls ready?

42:02.196 --> 42:03.837
I'll be late for school.

42:04.996 --> 42:06.437
Almost done.

42:07.156 --> 42:08.196
You insisted

42:08.277 --> 42:09.996
on having fried vegetable balls.

42:10.237 --> 42:13.476
This dish requires a lot of effort.

42:13.516 --> 42:14.556
We have to take it slow.

42:15.676 --> 42:16.437
It's ready.

42:17.717 --> 42:18.717
One.

42:19.237 --> 42:20.357
Two.

42:20.877 --> 42:21.797
Three.

42:22.357 --> 42:23.357
Four.

42:23.437 --> 42:24.437
Five.

42:24.636 --> 42:26.076
Lately, we don't know why,

42:26.596 --> 42:28.837
but the old lady keeps using
soil from flowerpots

42:28.877 --> 42:29.877
to make mud balls.

42:30.357 --> 42:32.277
She claims they're her vegetable balls.

42:34.596 --> 42:35.556
Flowerpot soil.

42:36.277 --> 42:38.516
If accidentally eaten, isn't it unsafe?

42:38.596 --> 42:39.957
At first, we were worried too.

42:40.317 --> 42:41.877
We tried taking the mud balls

42:42.076 --> 42:43.036
while she was asleep.

42:43.437 --> 42:44.717
But after waking up

42:44.877 --> 42:46.156
and finding them missing,

42:46.277 --> 42:47.237
she threw a tantrum.

42:47.676 --> 42:48.996
Said they were for her daughter.

42:49.036 --> 42:49.676
In the end,

42:49.917 --> 42:52.116
his wife still passed away.

42:52.196 --> 42:53.076
We realized

42:53.196 --> 42:54.397
she never actually ate them.

42:54.877 --> 42:56.277
So we let her be.

43:00.196 --> 43:01.357
Making vegetable balls?

43:01.757 --> 43:03.837
Why this sudden craving?

43:03.957 --> 43:04.957
Just felt like eating

43:05.556 --> 43:06.957
your homemade vegetable balls.

43:07.076 --> 43:08.317
Missing your cooking.

43:09.596 --> 43:09.996
Alright.

43:10.757 --> 43:11.317
Take a look.

43:12.277 --> 43:12.717
Enough?

43:13.476 --> 43:14.797
With this big bowl of yours,

43:15.116 --> 43:16.437
you could make five platters!

43:16.877 --> 43:17.556
First step,

43:17.757 --> 43:18.837
add white sugar.

43:19.437 --> 43:20.036
Adding sugar.

43:20.076 --> 43:21.596
To draw out moisture.

43:25.917 --> 43:26.797
Mix evenly, right?

43:27.116 --> 43:28.036
Of course!

43:28.116 --> 43:29.196
Need to repeat?

43:29.237 --> 43:30.676
Mix it.

43:31.357 --> 43:32.036
See?

43:32.516 --> 43:34.437
Told you to come to Jingzhou.

43:34.717 --> 43:36.156
I've said it many times.

43:36.797 --> 43:37.516
If you're here,

43:37.556 --> 43:38.996
you'd be sitting here with me,

43:39.076 --> 43:40.156
teaching me directly.

43:40.237 --> 43:41.317
I learn fast!

43:43.476 --> 43:44.516
You stay put.

43:44.556 --> 43:45.317
I'm not going.

43:45.397 --> 43:46.757
I'm busy now.

43:47.797 --> 43:48.957
These days,

43:49.156 --> 43:50.237
I'm busy playing mahjong.

43:51.156 --> 43:53.116
The neighborhood ladies say,

43:53.437 --> 43:54.636
"Madam, at your age,

43:54.757 --> 43:56.277
you should exercise your mind."

43:56.996 --> 43:57.917
Alright.

43:58.837 --> 43:59.957
I know

44:00.757 --> 44:03.156
you have an exciting senior life.

44:03.996 --> 44:05.996
I won't keep you

44:06.076 --> 44:07.437
from your joyful golden years.

44:08.237 --> 44:09.357
After mixing,

44:09.596 --> 44:10.676
drain the water.

44:10.797 --> 44:11.476
Then chop.

44:11.596 --> 44:13.116
After chopping, add seasoning.

44:13.357 --> 44:14.957
Chinese five-spice, allspice.

44:15.036 --> 44:16.116
And some salt.

44:16.237 --> 44:17.076
Also add eggs.

44:17.357 --> 44:18.676
Don't over-salt!

44:19.036 --> 44:19.676
Wait!

44:19.676 --> 44:20.516
Slow down!

44:20.596 --> 44:21.516
Speak slower.

44:21.596 --> 44:23.556
Slow down.

44:23.636 --> 44:25.237
My brain can't keep up with yours.

44:25.317 --> 44:27.277
You play Go and chess daily.

44:29.437 --> 44:31.717
So you forget things too?

44:32.757 --> 44:34.397
You used to complain about me.

44:34.757 --> 44:36.516
"You never remember what I tell you!"

44:37.196 --> 44:38.556
Now it's your turn.

44:39.837 --> 44:40.556
Yan.

44:44.496 --> 44:46.077
笙ｪLike fireworks that loved笙ｪ

44:46.197 --> 44:47.568
笙ｪRushing toward the stars笙ｪ

44:47.760 --> 44:49.712
笙ｪUndaunted by pain笙ｪ

44:51.169 --> 44:52.828
笙ｪFearless of flames笙ｪ

44:52.979 --> 44:56.349
笙ｪEven if just a fleeting sparkle笙ｪ

44:57.552 --> 44:59.216
笙ｪWe shed tears笙ｪ

44:59.216 --> 45:02.864
笙ｪDeep blue seas turn to foam笙ｪ

45:03.295 --> 45:05.872
笙ｪWe regained freedom笙ｪ

45:07.184 --> 45:09.328
笙ｪIf you remember me笙ｪ

45:09.872 --> 45:12.779
笙ｪThen I'm pleased笙ｪ

45:25.536 --> 45:29.680
笙ｪI just wanna take my time tonight笙ｪ

45:31.681 --> 45:35.971
笙ｪTo do all the things I said I'd try笙ｪ

45:37.696 --> 45:43.552
笙ｪI go surfing, go diving, go driving,
and go flying to a different place笙ｪ

45:44.032 --> 45:46.848
笙ｪI go drink, go party, and go dance笙ｪ

45:46.848 --> 45:50.176
笙ｪEven if I'm lonely笙ｪ

45:50.816 --> 45:55.552
笙ｪCause I just have been hurt
too many times笙ｪ

45:57.324 --> 46:01.562
笙ｪI'm giving it all to get nothing back笙ｪ

46:03.424 --> 46:08.576
笙ｪI was lost in the dark,
and it's too hurt to even see笙ｪ

46:09.664 --> 46:14.526
笙ｪSee the world and how it flows.
We never let go笙ｪ

46:16.256 --> 46:19.232
笙ｪSo I'll take my time笙ｪ

46:19.456 --> 46:22.624
笙ｪTo reignite笙ｪ

46:22.624 --> 46:27.649
笙ｪThe love I should deserve笙ｪ

46:29.291 --> 46:32.297
笙ｪWhen the time is right笙ｪ

46:32.297 --> 46:35.574
笙ｪYou realize笙ｪ

46:35.574 --> 46:40.204
笙ｪIt will all be alright笙ｪ

46:41.952 --> 46:46.636
笙ｪCause I just have been hurt
too many times笙ｪ

46:48.400 --> 46:52.686
笙ｪI'm giving it all to get nothing back笙ｪ

46:54.592 --> 47:00.303
笙ｪI was lost in the dark,
and it's too hurt to even see笙ｪ

47:00.991 --> 47:05.491
笙ｪSee the world and how it flows.
We never let go笙ｪ

47:07.424 --> 47:10.560
笙ｪSo I'll take my time笙ｪ

47:10.560 --> 47:13.792
笙ｪTo reignite笙ｪ

47:13.792 --> 47:18.760
笙ｪThe love I should deserve笙ｪ

47:20.224 --> 47:23.470
笙ｪWhen the time is right笙ｪ

47:23.470 --> 47:26.791
笙ｪYou realize笙ｪ

47:26.791 --> 47:31.248
笙ｪIt will all be alright笙ｪ
